channel.title: 317 DELTA - Players die upon loging in! Rep++
channel.description:
So anyone who logs on my server is hit with like 1-70 or 99 hp damage and dies.
Anyone know how to change that?
Rep++ for answers!

item.title: 317 DELTA - Players die upon loging in! Rep++
item.dc:creator: @JGX JGX
item.description:
@JGX wrote:

[quote=“Team_Rocket, post:2, topic:428532”]It’s one of these things:

  1. Something in your Processing methods.
  2. A glitch involving Jad where he attacks players.
  3. An anti-leech which I won’t help you with at all.[/quote]

It was a problem with my Jad. The problem is fixed now. Thank you all for your help. Rep++ to all of you.
